```

But this has the SAME problem - `Initialize` is an `async Task` and the outer `InitializeAndRun` creates a state machine that captures `ExecutionContext` before `await Initialize` and restores it after.

OK so the real approach needs to be: make `Initialize` NOT be a separate async method within `QuartzSchedulerThread`'s call chain, or combine the code so that `NewJob` and `Execute` happen in the same async method body.

